page.title: 11My Typical Weekend
page.content:
I get up and watch television.I like the Saturday Picture Show because it has cartoons and pop music.In the afternoon I sometimes go fishing with my friend Ian Burrows.We normally catch quite a lot.We use cheese for bait and we catch trout and eels.We have two piece fishing rods and we fish at Cannop Ponds which is near Parkend.I play football and last season I played for Yorkley Under 12's.We got a final but lost 1-0.In the 1985-86 season I will play for another local side at Elwood.
Jono Mould
Aged 11 years.
